thread.title: Transgender community stages protest in eastern India over rising rape incidents

title: Transgender community stages protest in eastern India over rising rape incidents
text:
Transgender community stages protest in eastern India over rising rape incidents 6:57am EDT - 01:15 
Members of the transgender community stage a protest condemning the rising number of rape and harrassment cases in the country. No reporter narration.
